data.text:
5.162 Wikipedia articles in 145 languages in which images from Category:Media contributed by Koninklijke Bibliotheek are used, grouped by language

This report was generated using the GLAMorousToHTML code. This Python script creates an HTML page, an Excel file and this Wiki page, listing all Wikipedia articles (in all languages) in which (one or more) images from a given category on Wikimedia Commons are used.

It uses this XML output of the GLAMorous tool d.d. 14-02-2024.

Also see the documentation of this tool. There you can also find out how to run the tool yourself.

Other formats

This report page is also available as a HTML-page on Github.

The raw data is available as an Excel file on Github. More structured data formats (csv, json) will be added in the future.

Contact

This report was made by Olaf Janssen, Wikimedia coordinator @KB, national library of the Netherlands. You can find my contact details on my Wikimedia user page or on my KB expert page.
